<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7510> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7510" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "A refugee from the proscriptions who became an officer under Sextus Pompeius (App. BC 4.43, and 84) in 42. In MRR 2.362, on Pompeius Bithynicus (26), note that the reading in App. BC 4.43, and 84 (#) should be retained. There is no evidence that this Hirtius was a senator.\n" .
